belaayaṭako abhyaasa khelamaa nepaalako lagaaṭaara ṭesro jiṭa

kaathamaadaun, saauna १

abhyaasa khelakaa laagi belaayaṭa bhramaṇamaa raheko nepaali raastriya kriketa tolile klaba kriketa kanphrensalaai (sisisi) chaara wiketale haraaeko chha । 

belaayaṭako laṇdanasṭhiṭa staanamora sisi maidaanamaa gaeraaṭi bhaeko khelamaa gharelu toli sisisilaai haraaepachhi nepaalale lagaaṭaara ṭesro jiṭa haaṭa paareko ho । tasa jiṭera byaatiŋa gareko sisisile nirdhaariṭa ५० obharamaa ७ wiketako ksaṭimaa २२६ rana banaaeko ṭhiyo । jawaaphi byaatiŋamaa āeko nepaalale ४६.१ obharamaa maaṭra chha wiketa gumaaundai laksya bhetaayo । 

nepaalako jiṭamaa kapṭaana paarasa khadkaale arḍhasaṭakiya paari kheldai sarwaadhika ६७ rana banaae । ṭyasṭai, anila maṇdalale ४३, upakapṭaana jñaanenḍra mallale ३६, saraḍa bhesawaakarale १९ ranako yogadaana die bhane awijiṭa rahandai toliko jiṭa nikaalekaa raaju rijaala ra raaju pulaamile kramasah wyakṭigaṭa १७ ra १६ rana jode । ṭyasaigari winoḍa bhaṇdaarile chha ṭaṭhaa saagara punale chaara rana banaae । 

yasaaghi sisisilaai rokne kramamaa nepaalakaa somapaala kaami ra sandipa laamichhaanele dui÷dui ṭaṭhaa kapṭaana paarasa ra karaṇa kesile eka÷eka wiketa lie । 

āgaami mahinaa neḍaralyaandasanga usakai gharelu maidaanamaa wiswa kriketa liga chyaampiyanasipa khelne ṭayaarimaa raheko nepaala ahile abhyaasa khelakaa laagi belaayaṭamaa chha । nepaala merolebona klabako nimṭomaa yasai saaṭaa landana gaeko ho । 

yasaaghi bhaekaa duwai khelamaa jiṭa nikaalne kramamaa nepaalale phri–phorestara klabalaai १२९ ranako wisaala anṭarale haraaeko ṭhiyo bhane indiyana jimakhaanaalaai २० ranale paakhaa lagaaeko ṭhiyo । raasasa